        "body": "After using callgrind to get a sense of **Glitter**'s performance, it's clear that opening the `git` repository takes most of the execution time.\r\n\r\nLooking closer at the interpreter as well, the majority of the instruction reach comes from cloning the vectors which hold the AST nodes.  A zero-copy implementation could still create a noticeable runtime improvement."
